USLocalizer - Class in T07

USPoller - Class in client
This class is the client-side version of the US Poller, it will poll the Ultrasonic sensor value, and process it through a mean filter getting both the raw value and the processed mean value as the result
USPoller(UltrasonicSensor) - Constructor for class client.USPoller
Construct the Ultrasonic poller with the ultrasonic sensor
USPoller - Class in T07
Class controls the US sensors of the robot, filters and processes data and control pinging of the sensors so US information is stable
